Lesson 3 = Crazy Czech Consonants! üá®üáø Pronunciation & Czech Alphabet ====================================================================================================================================================================
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v8udpCkbW1Q&list=PLa-iOaRNqZBx4H7bAmMvDEzr94yG0y6Ub&index=4&ab_channel=CzechwithKate%C5%99ina
Consants in Czech are divided into 3 easy groups :
  Hard = H / CH / K / R / D / T / N 
  Soft = C / ƒå / J / ≈ò / ≈† / ≈Ω / ƒé
  Ambiguous = B / F / L / M / P / S / V / Z























